<h3 id="photos-bulks-up">Photos Bulks Up</h3>

<p>Apple added numerous features to Photos, refactoring its interface to
match the update in Catalina. It now provides an AI-curated selection of
photos displayed by Years, Months, and Daysâ€”complete with event
titlesâ€”plus an All Photos grid that shows everything. Live Photos and
