<h3 id="health-adds-cycle-tracking-and-fertility">Health Adds Cycle Tracking and Fertility</h3>

<p>On the iPhone, the Health app at long last gains features related to
cycle tracking and fertility. Using data entered or imported from a
third-party app, Health can now predict the start and end of a womanâ€™s
next three cycles and provide a notification when her period is
approaching. Similarly, it can predict fertility windows and pop up an
alert when one is approaching. Cycle Tracking, a companion Apple Watch
app, will make it easier to log menstruation and symptoms.</p>

<p>iOS 13â€™s Health app also now tracks headphone audio levels and alerts
